######################
Landslide for Novapost
######################

This repository contains base material to use `landslide`_ slides generator
with a custom theme for `Novapost`_.


*****
Usage
*****

.. warning::

    Please make sure that you have access to Novapost VPN, or install will
    probably break.

* Download this repository
* Install with ``make install``
* Create/edit :file:`src/index.rst`
* Generate slides with ``make slides``
* Open generated :file:`var/slides.html` with your favorite browser

.. note::

   Slides are generated in embed mode, i.e. everything you need to carry is the
   generated ".html" file.


**********
References
**********

.. _`landslide`: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/landslide
.. _`Novapost`: http://www.novapost.fr
